mandatory Class I Federal Areas. 
EPA is also proposing to correct its error in failing to accurately reflect Colorado's Visibility SIP approval status
in a previous action on the State's Visibility protection provisions. 


IV. Request for Public Comments


EPA is requesting comments on all aspects of this proposal. As indicated at the outset of this document, EPA will consider
