percent efficiency compared to a 98 percent efficiency achieved by thermal destruction (combustion) devices (e.g.,
flares, enclosed flares, and thermal and catalytic incinerators). Additional information and descriptions of
these control technologies are found in the TSD for this rulemaking (see 

